        h2#instructions Instructions:
        p Use the moving game board with 8 doors to play the game.
        h3#rules Rules:
        ul
          li Click on the doors to find the treasure.
          li You only get 4 chances. There is a counter for you so you can keep track of the doors you've opened and the doors you have remaining.
          li Pay attention to the alert window on this page and follow the instructions as they appear.
          li
            strong Find the treasure!
        h3#clues Clues:
        ol
          li There are tree emojis, which mean you are still safe to proceed to the next door.
          li There are bomb emojis, which is game over and you will need to restart the game.
          li There is a rainbow emoji, which means you win.
          li
            strong SIDE NOTE:
            | Once a door is opened the shape of the square changes. Be careful these doors are shaking rather fast!
        table border="4" style=("height: 100px; width: 100px;")
